.name
StScan
.type
Image Processing
.short
scanning software for Siemens ST400 SCSI scanner
.version
1.0
.date
91.10.15
.restrictions
Only standard OCS video modes without overscan supported, writes directly into bitplanes
.requirements
SCSI interface supporting direct scsi command;
enough contigous RAM for a whole image (min. 2MB recommended)
.construction
Aztec C 5.0
.tested
A2000 Rev 6.2 + A2091/2MB + A2630/4MB + A2320 + Siemens ST400; Kick/WB 1.3
.distribution
Freeware
